    "name": "Josephine (14)",
    "profile": "Josephine found something to say and a way to say it. Lithium Records picked on this in 2000, and things happened - records were released, radio stations played them, television programmes showed them, magazines and newspapers wrote about them. Radio 1 voted them Session of the Year 2001. Jockrock voted them Best Newcomers 2002. T in the Park was 2004, Best of T Break next. Then in 2005 they met Bracken Records, and got married. It was a big step, but things are harmonious. The first offspring is expected August 22nd 2005. Things look happening.",
